# =============================================================================
# Sentinel Insight — environment variables (TEMPLATE)
# =============================================================================
#
# Copy this file to `.env` (same directory) and fill in the real values.
# `.env` is in .gitignore and never committed.
#
#   cp .env.example .env
#   $EDITOR .env
#
# All variables below are read by:
#   - analysis/summarizer.py   (chat completions via OpenAI)
#   - audio/transcriber.py     (Whisper transcription via OpenAI)
#   - audio/voice_analyzer.py  (reuses summarizer's OpenAI setup)
#
# If OPENAI_API_KEY is missing or invalid, the Insight UI still loads but:
#   - voice transcription returns an error
#   - LLM emotion analysis falls back to the local keyword-based analyzer
#     (27 regex patterns, weights 1/2/3) — degraded but functional
#   - the multimodal summarizer returns "⚠️ LLM unavailable"
# =============================================================================

# ── OpenAI API key (required for full functionality) ───────────────────────
# Get one at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Format: sk-proj-... or sk-...
# Scopes needed: standard usage of /v1/chat/completions and /v1/audio/transcriptions
# Pricing: pay-as-you-go (charged per request); no free tier as of 2026.
#
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-paste-your-openai-key-here
